        <Parent_String>earth dams [300006107], dams by construction [300006106], dams (hydraulic structures) [300006084], hydraulic structures by function [300006112], hydraulic structures [300006073], single built works by function [300004894], single built works by specific type [300004795], single built works (built environment) [300004790], Single Built Works (hierarchy name) [300004789], Built Environment (hierarchy name) [300264550], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
        <Hier_Rel_Type>Genus/Species-BTG</Hier_Rel_Type>
